ctical application, and highlights the potential for profitable trading.**## Arb
itrage\n\n### Inter-exchange arbitrage\n\nInter-exchange arbitrage opportunities
arise when the same event is priced differently across multiple platforms. The m
ain idea is to capture the right moment by buying a contract on the platform whe
re its price (implied probability) is lower and selling it where the price is hi
gher. The difference between these prices is referred to as the inter-exchange s
pread and typically exists only for a short period due to the rapid reactions of
