n markets) had implications for the properties of its prices. We believe our res
ults show that these two questions are related.Our model, while simple, illustra
tes how Kalshi\'s market microstructure encourages there to be a favorite-longsh
ot bias and influences the form this takes for both Makers and Takers.\n\nWe hav
